com.yworks.yfiles.layout.tree

Class FreeNodePlacer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.tree.AbstractRotatableNodePlacer
      • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.tree.FreeNodePlacer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFromSketchNodePlacer, INodePlacer

    public class FreeNodePlacer
extends AbstractRotatableNodePlacer
    A FreeNodePlacer is a simple pseudo-placer.

    The children of local root nodes are not moved. The INodePlacer just merges their rotated shapes and routes the edges.

    This INodePlacer may be useful if a local root node does not have any children or you want to place them manually.
